snippet.title: Margot Robbie Hangs with Amber Heard After Her Divorce Settlement
snippet.description:
Margot Robbie stops by the Rolling Stones exhibit with a group of pals last week in London, England.

Among those in the group were Margot‘s boyfriend Tom Ackerley, Cara Delevingne (not pictured), and Amber Heard, who had just settled her divorce from Johnny Depp earlier in the week.

Later, Margot, Cara, Amber, and their buddies grabbed dinner at Ivy Kensington Brassiere. The group also hit up Chiltern Firehouse that night, after getting denied entry to a nightclub in Marylebone, E! News reports.

20+ pictures inside of Margot Robbie and others…
